snippet.title: Rapid Angel (1998) Playthrough (PS1)
snippet.description:
Ooh, you thought I was gonna do a runthrough of Wolf Fang on the Playstation? Maybe another time. But anyways, here comes another PSX runthrough, this is for Rapid Angel released on August 13th, 1998. This game is platformer/beat ‘em up where you have to deliver the goods to a certain location while you beat up bad guys and plenty of platforming. The graphics are good, decent music and you have unlimited continues. Definitely worth a shot. 

All rights belong to Techno Soleil and MonkeyPaw Games.
